	* Makefile.am (install-exec-hook): Use APIVERSION.
	* m4/init.m4 (AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE): Use am__api_version.
	* m4/amversion.in (AM_AUTOMAKE_VERSION): Set am__api_version from
	APIVERSION.
